The Beginning~
Welcome to the Realms of Kuvia! If you have just completed making your first
character, congratulations. This is The Beginning, the start of every
character's journey in this dangerous and exciting world. You are still a
novice, and have lessons to learn before you are ready to go and interact with
your fellow players and the world around you. Read each room description for
important information on what to do next. Proceed north by typing 'north' into
your prompt and pressing enter or return. Words in '' are commands. You may
type 'exit' at any time to see available exits. Also, by typing 'autoexit',
exits will automatically be displayed when you enter a room.
~
