The Path of Enlightenment: Nourishment~
Congratulations on having mastered your fears. Buried within fears are your
expectations, and what more could you expect from a well-fought battle than a
good meal? Lo, a kipling pie appeared in the corpse of the leech! Food and
water are both healthy parts of a complete breakfast, and essential to your
survival. Your hit points, mana, and movements will regenerate much slower when
you are hungry or thirsty, so take the time to eat up! You must hold an item to
'eat' it or 'drink' from it.
